{"word":"ἀσχήμων","slug":"ἀσχήμων","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀσχήμων</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:σχῆμα'><el>σχῆμα</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>misshapen, unseemly, shameful</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>turpis</el>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>of persons, <el>ἀσχ. γενέσθαι</el> to be <i>indecorous</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}